title: My 15 Books - May 2014 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 15 books for this month, 9 ePUBs and 6 PDFs:


01. Beer, Food, and Flavor - A Guide to Tasting, Pairing, and the Culture of Craft Beer
02. Creating Stylish & Sexy Photography
03. Drawing Lab for Mixed-Media Artists - 52 Creative Exercises to Make Drawing Fun
04. Handbook of Decision Analysis
05. Lubricants - Introduction to Properties and Performance
06. More Food From Small Spaces - Growing Denser Deeper Higher Longer Vegetable Gardens
07. Neeb's Fundamentals of Mental Health Nursing, 4th ed
08. Pies and Tarts with Heart - Expert Pie-Building Techniques for 60+ Sweet and Savory Vegan Pies
09. Sound Visualization and Manipulation
10. Space Science Cover-Ups - The Truth about the Moon, Mars and More
11. Obstacle Race Training - How to Beat Any Course, Compete Like a Champion and Change Your Life
12. The Handbook of Solitude - Psychological Perspectives on Social Isolation, Social Withdrawal, and Being Alone
13. The Mountain Man Cookbook
14. The Shredded Chef - 120 Recipes for Building Muscle, Getting Lean, and Staying Healthy
15. Vodka Politics - Alcohol, Autocracy, and the Secret History of the Russian State
